		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It would be nice, wouldn't it?  We really need it.  Every time I've patched something into the forum I've ended up having to do a lot of it manually.. patches on top of patches, etc, it's kind of a pain.
<br />
<br />Actually it's a thought I had recently.. not long ago I purchased some web hosting.  One thing I'd really like to do with it is set up a file uploading area that we could all use.  Kind of like <a href="http://2a03.free.fr/" class="postlink">http://2a03.free.fr/</a>, but for more than music.  It would be immensely useful.  If anyone could point out a particular software package I could look at, I'd definitely be interested in installing it.  I don't even know where to look.

		

